{
  "stem": "22047.1",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And then he was assigned to-- [PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] I can't think of the name of the fort he was assigned to on the East Coast.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Fort Ethan Allen, Vermont.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "That's where he was assigned.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And he-- he and my mother spent three years at that camp.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Then he-- he went to Japan on General MacArthur's staff in 1951, well after the war.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And came back in '54 and retired from the military.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And a year later my mother passed away.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And so he-- he spent his retirement years in-- in Woodland Hills in Southern California and in Canoga Park.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "He remarried after my mother passed away, about two years later, and spent almost-- well, the rest of his retirement years until he passed away in-- in '75, '76.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And that's essentially what my dad did.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "He was a-- a career officer, a career military man.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Strict.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Let me tell you about a-- it was an experience that I'll never forget.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was in the ROTC at Van Nuys High School, and of course, he was the-- he was the officer in charge there.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we were vying to become officers in the ROTC.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so we had to go through these drills, and I was assigned this day to be a leader of one of the platoons, and he was the so-called company commander.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so he gave these commands, and I gave the-- he said, company mass left.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I said, continue to march, and he said, as you were.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Finally, after the third time, he said, Dunn, what is the proper command when I give the command company mass left?",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I said, sir, is it not continue to march and then half left march?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
